text: The prime minister of the State of Palestine is the head of government of the State of Palestine. The post was created in January 2013, when the Palestinian National Authority was officially renamedhttps://www.algemeiner.com/2013/01/04/abbas-signs-decree-to-change-pa- name-to-%E2%80%98state-of-palestine%E2%80%99/ into the State of Palestine.
